reviewText: love it bought for mom for mothers day shes been looking for the Jewel movie on dvd since it was release in 2001 wished it was just that movie without others but I know she won't care

Bought this for the Farrah Fawcett/Cicely Tyson movie "Jewel"....this DVD is worth the price for this movie alone. A good family film. Highly recommended!
Farrah Fawcett and Cicely Tyson are wonderful in Jewel.  Very touching and makes you tear up
